Implementation of Matlab tic() command

Source: R/ubiquity.R
tic.Rd

Used in conjunction with toc() to find the elapsed time when code is executed.

Usage

tic(type = c("elapsed", "user.self", "sys.self"))

Arguments

type

can be either "elapsed" "user.self" or "sys.self"

Value

time tic was called

See also

toc

Examples

tic()
Sys.sleep(3)
toc()
#> elapsed 
#>   3.008
